Hi everybody! I'm finally opening up about my loose skin situation after losing 250 pounds and coming back to the internet with the Two Steps Ahead video. Many people assumed I had already gone through skin removal, but the truth is, I had not. Today I show you how much loose skin is actually on my body and also show you the results of getting a 360 body lift last week, otherwise known as a circumferential lift, aka a belt lipectomy, along with an abdominoplasty with muscle plication (muscle repair). I spent a lot of time researching the best doctors and I decided to choose Dr. Katzen. He exceeded my expectations, and I hope some of you pick him as your doctor, too! I hope this inspires anybody who's on the fence about getting post weight-loss procedures. It's been one of the, if not THE most rewarding thing I've ever done for myself. I feel brand new and free! You get one life and one body. It's time to chase your dreams.
